name: Queen Medb (Fate/Grand Order)
description:
Medb from Fate Grand Order. This is my very first LoRa so please be nice (though I think it turned out pretty good).

If you use this LoRa, please show your results! I'm very interested in seeing them.

No alternate outfits for now, will be included in the next version.

All sample pictures were generated with Meinamix 8
I recommend using weight of 0.5
Add the tag 'medb \(fate\)'.

First Ascension:
(Positive): cloak, white cloak, fur trim, thigh boots,
(Optional): fur-trimmed cloak, fur-trimmed boots,

Second Ascension:
(Positive): pauldrons, shoulder armor,
(Negative): navel, midriff,

Third Ascension:
No special promts required

Extra tips:
-Sometimes it generates blue eyes instead of the brownish-yellow she has, so I use "blue eyes" as a negative prompt.
-It can generate the whip she usually holds if you add the tags "holding whip, whip, riding crop", but it's hard to get a nice one.
-Sometimes she will appear bare handed, adding "gauntlets" to the prompt prevents that.
